'''Qaresi Squadron''' was a [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] [[Squadron/Legends|squadron]], equipped with [[X-wing starfighter/Legends|X-wing starfighters]], that was assigned to the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] warship [[Bounty (warship)|''Bounty'']] during the [[Second Galactic Civil War]]. It participated in Alliance operations monitoring [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] fleet movements in the [[Both system|Bothawui system]].

